{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0157e66495","title":"给邵华的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec5dea2a63","index":0,"year":1962,"month":6,"day":3,"articleId":"0157e66495"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1f9c6f35f0","type":"title","text":"给部华\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"50dc2370b5","type":"paragraph","text":"你好！有信，拿来，想看。要好生养病，立志奔前程，女儿气要少些，加一点男儿气，为社会做一番事业，企予望之。《上邪》一篇，要多读。余不尽。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"24896671c9","type":"subtitle","text":"父亲","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"70c6c6e829","type":"paragraph","text":"六月三日上午七时","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"131bdb5738","type":"paragraph","text":"邵华，原名张少华，毛泽东的儿娘。毛泽东写给她的这封信无上款","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"ca9012a861","type":"paragraph","text":"指毛岸青、邵华各自写给毛泽东的信。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"},{"id":"f1dc6f46be","type":"paragraph","text":"《上邪》，乐府汉《镜歌》十八曲之一。上，指天；邪，通“耶”，语气词。上邪，指关为普的意思。其词为：“上邪！我欲与君相知，长命无绝衰。山无陵，江水为竭，冬雷震震，夏雨雪，天地合，乃敢与君绝。”","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495"}],"page":{"id":"1be8789c47","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"0157e66495","start":147,"end":147}}}},"__N_SSG":true}